    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Dad did you get that leaky faucet in the fellowship hall fixed? Roger said he noticed it dripping on Sunday."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1754200800",
    "from_id": "1",
    "message_id": "1000001",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Fixed it Tuesday. Had to drive to Runnings for the right washer. Dale came along, made a whole morning of it."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1756710000",
    "from_id": "2",
    "message_id": "1000002",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Of course he did \ud83d\ude04 You two eat at Koffee Kup after?"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1759478400",
    "from_id": "3",
    "message_id": "1000003",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Where else."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1762160400",
    "from_id": "4",
    "message_id": "1000004",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Emma wants to know if you're coming Sunday. She's doing the children's message."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000001",
    "date": "1764928800",
    "from_id": "5",
    "message_id": "1000005",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Wouldn't miss it. Tell her I'll be the one in the back with the broom."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1767610800",
    "from_id": "6",
    "message_id": "1000006",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Roger. Got a slow drain in the church kitchen and the snake I have here won't reach. You still got that 25-footer in your garage?"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1770379200",
    "from_id": "7",
    "message_id": "1000007",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Yeah it's out there. I can drop it by after work, around 5."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1773147600",
    "from_id": "8",
    "message_id": "1000008",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "No need to drive over. Just leave it out front and I'll swing by after my shift."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1791640800",
    "from_id": "9",
    "message_id": "1000009",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Works for me. Fair warning though \u2014 Karen'll probably rope you into staying for supper."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1794409200",
    "from_id": "10",
    "message_id": "1000010",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Worse things could happen. Tell her I'll bring the coffee cake Dale made me take from Koffee Kup this morning."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000002",
    "date": "1797091200",
    "from_id": "11",
    "message_id": "1000011",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Ha. She'll take it. See you around 5 then Gary."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1752512400",
    "from_id": "12",
    "message_id": "1000012",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Jeff. Tyler still coming Saturday? Dale's gonna be at the Koffee Kup around 8 if he wants to tag along. Figured he might get a kick out of it."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1755280800",
    "from_id": "13",
    "message_id": "1000013",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Yeah he's coming, bus gets in around 6:30. You okay picking him up or should he grab a ride?"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1757790000",
    "from_id": "14",
    "message_id": "1000014",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "I'll be up by then anyway. Does he eat eggs? Got a dozen off the Narvesons last week, more than I need."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1760558400",
    "from_id": "15",
    "message_id": "1000015",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Dad he eats everything, you don't have to cook. He's 16 not 6 \ud83d\ude04"
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1763240400",
    "from_id": "16",
    "message_id": "1000016",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "Not trouble. Tell him bring work gloves too. I got the Bethlehem fellowship hall chairs to restain this week, could use an extra set of hands Friday if he's game."
  },
  {
    "chat_id": "2000003",
    "date": "1766008800",
    "from_id": "17",
    "message_id": "1000017",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0",
    "text": "He'll think that's great honestly. I'll tell him. Thanks dad."
